      "title": "Six people sentenced to death 22 years after five people were shot dead in 2000",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Six people were sentenced to death after they were convicted of murdering five people in Devinuawara in 2000.",
        "Matara High Court Judge Thamara Thennakoon ordered the death sentences after the six accused were guilty of shooting five people.",
        "Five people were brutally shot dead in 2000, when a group opened fire at their van in Devinuwara.",
        "15 people were arrested over the murders, and five of them were acquitted and released.",
        "Six people sentenced to death 22 years after five people were shot dead in 2000"
